The map can only be played 1 on 1.

Each player has 20 weapons on his side. 2 AWPs, 2 scouts and 12 grenades among the cards, whoever takes them will be stronger.

If you notice a flaw in the map or want to suggest an idea, write to the creator of the map in discord.Â  I will be glad to everyone :-D

The map is similar to the standard famous Cbble map, but only a mini version of it. Good luck having fun with your friend on this wonderful and marvelous map!
